# Inject source for workspace-dispatch epic (Trello `jAdeJgi5`).
#
# Phase 2 (Trello `VKJzZjk9`) creates this directory so the inject
# pipeline has somewhere to mirror workspace trees FROM. Phase 3 adds
# the first fixture (`issue-worker/`), Phase 4 adds `slack-worker/`,
# Phase 5 adds `http-launch-default/`.
#
# Each subdirectory `<name>/` is a full workspace tree matching the
# layout `src/workspace/resolve.ts` expects: `workspace.yml`,
# `.mcp.json`, `allowed-tools.txt`, `.claude/settings.json`, plus any
# `.claude/rules/*.md`, `.claude/skills/*/SKILL.md`, `.claude/tools/*`,
# `.claude/agents/*.md`, and a project-root `CLAUDE.md`.
#
# `injectDanxWorkspaces` in `src/poller/index.ts` mirrors each subtree
# into every connected repo's `.danxbot/workspaces/<name>/` on every
# poll tick (idempotent + pruning).
